  "body": "<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j2f3jmM.png\" alt=\"Winter Overhaul Workmark\">\n\n<div>\n    <p><br><br></p>\n    <center>\n        <a href=\"https://discord.gg/sGwxnFV\">\n            <img width=\"10%\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/T4ltmGW.png\" alt=\"Discord\">\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Joosh7889\">\n            <img width=\"10%\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ewzK3Zb.png\" alt=\"Twitter\">\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCUvb1-kBGDEA1gVtd3UhlLg/videos\">\n            <img width=\"10%\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EirVdtZ.png\" alt=\"YouTube\">\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/bonsaistudios\">\n            <img width=\"10%\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AEfwGvx.png\" alt=\"Kofi\">\n        </a>\n    </center>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n    <p><br><br></p>\n    <center>\n        <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/52LU4mv.png\" alt=\"About\">\n        <h4>Winter was developed for the MMD 2021 WinterJam. Winter Overhaul will update Minecraft's snowy biomes with new winter-related features!</h4>\n        <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/lXrggZqaE60\"\n                title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share\"\n                allowfullscreen></iframe>\n    </center>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n    <p><br><br></p>\n    <center>\n        <h3>Content</h3>\n    </center>\n    <center>\n        <img width=\"50%\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/5M97aUS6/images/a4f4de22f38f3bb1c6423e6c3343a7bda80a1e95.png\" alt=\"Headwear\">\n        <h5>Wear them yourself or give them to a snow golem to unlock various new abilities!</h5>\n    </center>\n    <center>\n        <img width=\"50%\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/5M97aUS6/images/5f16cd5d8370b8640d6f7e69a263e2ca46fd9a82.png\" alt=\"Headwear\">\n        <h5>Snow golems will now spawn with a random combination of arms, buttons, and faces - Over 1000 variations!</h5>\n    </center>\n    <center>\n        <img width=\"50%\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/5M97aUS6/images/90b8d119b2f9983224f88b23bec6e09907f92eaa.png\" alt=\"Headwear\">\n        <h5>They like sweet berries &lt;3</h5>\n    </center>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n    <p><br></p>\n    <center>\n        <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mnnbI3S.png\" alt=\"Credits\">\n        <p><br></p>\n        <dl>\n            <dt>Josh/Joosh - Art</dt>\n            <dt>ThatGravyBoat - Developer</dt>\n        </dl>\n    </center>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n    <p><br></p>\n    <center>\n        <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZtjUq8p.png\" alt=\"Our Other Projects\">\n        <p><br></p>\n        <dl>\n            <dt><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/creeper-overhaul\">Creeper Overhaul</a> - A mod that replaces the vanilla creeper with a variety of different biome-specific creeper types!</dt>\n            <dt><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/creatures-and-beasts\">Creatures and Beasts</a> - A mod that adds amazing creatures into Minecraft!</dt>\n            <dt><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/critters-and-companions\">Critters and Companions</a> - A mod which adds a variety of friendly animals!</dt>\n        </dl>\n    </center>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n    <center>\n        <a href=\"https://server.pro/?ref=joosh\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NDteLeV.png\" alt=\"Server.pro\"></a>\n    </center>\n</div>",
